author: Ed Kilgore
title: Trump Throws Brian Kemp Under the Bus on Business Reopenings - New York Magazine
description: The Georgia governor thought he was following the president’s wishes by quickly reopening Georgia businesses. But Trump zigged when Kemp zagged.
content: An odd new development has arisen in the complicated relationship between Donald J. Trump and his onetime acolyte, Georgia governor Brian Kemp. On Wednesday, the president rebuked Kemp for getting too far out in front of his campaign to reopen the economy wit… [+4893 chars]
